article_title: Wharton Study Demonstrates Why Obamacare Exchanges Are Floundering

article_metadata.description: A new Wharton study shows that except for those who are heavily subsidized, Obamacare coverage is a really bad deal for the uninsured. It's no wonder the Exchanges are projected to enroll only half as many people in 2016 as the CBO projected merely 4 months ago.
article_metadata.author: The Apothecary
